    "Also, AYDIN [92] trained and compared six ML architectures, called RF, Naı¨ve Bayes (NB), LR, K-nearest neighbor (KNN), MLP, and SVM, for the detection of T4SEs utilizing 10 types of chosen characteristics and fivefold cross-validation.",
